"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/114586","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2014-12-18","<p>Confirmed student numbers for 2014/15 and future years are not yet available. The Higher Education Statistics Agency will publish data on Higher Education entrants and enrolments for 2014/15 in January 2016.</p><p> </p>","Tunbridge Wells","Greg Clark","213632","2014-12-18T16:55:38.71Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/114586/answer","Biography information for Greg Clark","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/114586/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/114586/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2014-11-05","Higher Education: Admissions","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, when his Department plans to publish updated student numbers as a result of the abolition of the cap on student numbers.","false","Biography information for Liam Byrne","Birmingham, Hodge Hill","Mr Liam Byrne","213631"
